album.title: NOW That's What I Call Music Vol. 38

wiki.content: The F**kin' Perfect Songfacts says The track opens with Pink declaring that despite all her flaws, she's "still around." Once she gets to the chorus, the potty-mouthed singer comes over all motivational and tells the listener that they should look past their imperfections and see themselves as "F---in' Perfect."
